overview: Like fine wine, some women only get better with age. In Lesbian Beauties Vol. 5: Mature Women, Sweetheart Video pays homage to some of the most legendary female performers in adult entertainment - as well as a few mature "newbies." Written and directed by Nica Noelle.
title: Lesbian Beauties 5: Mature Women
